dc_title_s: Brazil--south coast, Baía da Ilha Grande--eastern part (terminal of Ilha Guaiba) (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: reproduction of Brazilian Chart 1621, 2nd edition, October 31, 1990 ... with the Brazilian Directorate of Hydrography and Navigation. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours, hachures, and spot heights. "From Brazilian Navy surveys to 1983." "Brazilian copyright law applies." "Soundings in meters." Includes tidal information.
